name: 玛塞奈·丽奈特
name_full: 玛塞奈·丽奈特 Marcenae Lynette
introduction: Marcenae Lynette, is an American Actress, originally from Alabama known for her appearances in NBC's Good Girls' as Elaine, Val, in 'Love IS__' and her memorable work on Black Lightning.She is writing, directing, and producing on multiple projects.Marcenae can also be found in new hit movies, The Georgetown Project, The Valet, and Help Wanted.
